After our investigation on some three-particle W -class states, the most distinct difference is that the quantum discord is not always larger than the EOF for the three-particle W class state under the phase ï¬‚ip channel. As a contrast, in Fig. 3 we ï¬nd that in an ideal environment, the quantum discord is greater than or equal to the EOF invariably. The relation between quantum discord and EOF under decoherence is shown in Fig. 4.
